description:
uFaber's faculty member has been preparing candidates for the CFA exams for over 8 years, and knows what it's like to balance work with the demanding CFA exams. uFaber will help you make the most of your revision time with this comprehensive set of video lectures.

Everything you need to get best of this course, is included in it. You shall learn all you need to know about fixed income securities in over 25 lectures and 4 hours of content!

Though course is prepared for CFA Candidates, anyone who wants to learn about fixed income securities, will benefit from it.
title: CFA Level 1 Fixed Income Securities (Dec 2016)
